Grammy winner Wizkid has announced a collaboration with award-winning singer Asa. The Nation’s recalled seven years ago, Wizkid had tweeted that Asa was the only artist he wanted to collaborate with ‘so badly’.   Simi explains absence from Nigerian idol for two weeks     Mr Macaroni: stop asking when I’ll get married     Victor Okhai is head judge for 8th AMVCAs   The tweet from 2015 by Wizkid reads: “Yo Asa has to be the only one I want to work with so bad! Love love her.’ Precisely seven years after the tweet, the ‘Essence’ singer confirmed his collaboration with Asa. - Advertisement - He tweeted: “ASA x BIG WIZ.”